NAME

    Device::Chip::From::Sensirion - a collection of chip drivers for
    Sensirion sensors

DESCRIPTION

    This distribution contains a number of Device::Chip drivers for various
    sensor chips manufactured by Sensirion.

    It also acts as a base class, providing common functionality for
    often-used operations.

METHODS

 get_serial_number

       $bytes = await $chip->get_serial_number;

    Returns a 6-byte encoding of the chip's internal serial number.

AUTHOR

    Paul Evans <leonerd@leonerd.org.uk>

